  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "Sennen Kazoku is a Game Boy Advance video game released in 2005 by Nintendo and Indieszero. The game was released exclusively in Japan. In the game, you'll play as Cupid, who was ordered to watch over a family by god. As Cupid, you must make sure that the family is protected through the generations.\n\nThe title was officially romanized in Super Smash Bros. Brawl.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb"
